<h2>Week 5: Developing the Server Side</h2>
<h4>Learning Objectives</h4>
<hr />
<p>Upon completion of this week, you will be able to:</p>
<ol>
<li>Identify what a web server needs to do.</li>
<li>Create a web server using JavaScript and Node.js.</li>
<li>Store lots of data persistently over a long time into a database --a Postgres database.</li>
<li>Understand the limitations of the server-side.</li>
</ol>
